channel.title: Player Owned Ports
channel.description: Are the only reason I log in recently. Hadn't logged in for a while before this update, but this is fun. It's not grindy and only takes like 5-10 minutes at a time. I love this sort of stuff. Haven't failed a single voyage yet, and while I usually only get 3-4 rounds off per day (of 2 ships, so 6-8 voyages), it's still fun. Can't wait to see some of the high tier gear.

item.description:
@3lv3n_snip3r wrote:

[quote=“KroniKz_, post:4, topic:472933”]Oh I love this update, I have already started working on it for my rsps. I will probably release.

Ot: very great update.[/quote]

Good luck.

OT: It’s a great update. The further you go, the more islands you can unlock. One you unlock the Skull region, you have a chance of getting scrolls for the armors/food that you can make. The armors are better than the Nex armors and the food is the best food currently in RuneScape. I think Jagex is trying to lower the price of the Nex armors so more people can afford it by releasing better armor.
